data.description: Great investment opportunity or a homeowner for customization in this ranch-style home.  No HOA.  Located about 20 mins to Tims Ford Lake and Jack Daniel Distillery.  With 3 beds, 2 baths, and a 2-car garage featuring additional backyard storage, this property offers both functionality and potential. Cozy wood burning fireplace and large living room and extra sun room to offer a great layout of the home.  Back on Market due to buyer financing fell thru.
